INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('1153a1587ba74ed28d63b7975610a30b', 'd6174743f4694ef39710ea3715c50efb', '9ed2ca0c740e46e3a4a5184f477acf64', '3', '1', '4位老人新西兰南岛20天3400公里的自驾之旅', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其实今天没啥好写的，一切都在计划中，都在预料中。本来觉得往东南飞嘛，很快就会天亮，可是</span><a class=\"bbsLmLabel\" href=\"https://z.qyer.com/deal/90455/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); display: inline; height: auto; left: auto; margin-right: 2px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-decoration-line: none; top: auto; width: auto;\">飞机</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">外面一直是黑的，后来才发现，舷窗的颜色是可调的。经过十几小时的飞行，飞机正点到达基督城机场。本来很担心入境时被查，网上很多告诫甚至警告，做攻略时入境卡怎么填写就很纠结，保险起见，带的所有药品都有医生的处方，登山鞋在入境单上也打了勾，生怕带了什么违禁物品（入境</span><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2EJZFFvBzRTYFI-/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">卡什</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">么填后面会细说），以至于上了飞机后还把一次性</span><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2MJYFFuBz9TZg/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">筷子</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">丢掉了。</span><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其实。。。其实什么都没有发生。。。。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">忘记为了什么，当我们入境时已经人不多了。入境官只是在入境单药品和登山鞋打钩的地方做了些标记，就放行了，没有开包检查，也没有看到其他人被开包检查，一个都没有。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">程程已经在等候我们了。这次出游的第一天全靠程程帮忙，出国有人接机的感觉真好，谢谢程程。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">本来我们预定的车是RAV4，属于中型SUV，可是到了停车场看到的是逍客，属于小型车了，当时心情就很不爽，有被骗的感觉。和<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"http://z.qyer.com/car/?utm_source=c03729731-pc&utm_medium=partner&utm_campaign=article&utm_content=%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">租车</a>公司联系后答复，老板故意给调整了一辆空间大的车，这不是胡扯吗。现在已经是下班时间了，又是周末，换车的话还不知道要等到什么时候，还好行李能勉强放得下，只好凑付开了，后来还车时经过交涉给我们退了133纽币。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;拿到车后简单检查了一下，就上路了，在南半球开右舵车的第一次就这么奉献了。由于在国内做了充分的准备，开右舵车也没觉得有特别不适应，就是有时雨刷和转向灯开始的时候容易弄反（关于开车后面有专门攻略）。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">接下来就是入住酒店、去超市购物和吃晚饭了，程程请我们在一家<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/china/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国</a>餐馆吃了一顿丰盛的晚餐，没想到这顿晚餐成了我们20天最奢侈的一顿。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们的住宿主要是在<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com%2F%3F%26aid%3D355694%26si%3Dai%252Cco%252Cci%252Cre%252Cdi%26label%3Dguid__datetime_15355794134793_aaid_355694-post-keyword%26lang%3Dzh-cn%26ifl%3D%26ss%3D&hotel_name=Booking.com+%E7%BC%A4%E5%AE%A2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">Booking</a>上预定的。关于住宿网上的介绍很多，有便宜的也有贵的，本游记就不做专门介绍了，关于超市后面会有介绍。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;\">今天的路线，从右上角基督城到左边的蒂卡波湖，总共230公里。住Lake Tekapo Motels &amp; Holiday Park (特卡波湖汽车旅馆和假日公园)。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;刚到蒂卡波，还没入住，先欣赏下美景。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;蒂卡波湖“既是湖的名字也是小镇的名字。小镇的北面是碧绿的湖水，湖对岸就是雄伟的南阿尔卑斯山。岩石粉顺着山上的冰河流入湖内，悬浮在湖中，使<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/lake-tekapo/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">蒂卡普湖</a>呈现出浓郁的碧绿色。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">毛利人是最早居住在麦肯奇盆地的人。他们用石头作为工具，捕捞鳗鱼，捕猎鸟类，沿河岸和湖岸建立了许多夏季营地。直到19世纪中叶一个叫麦肯奇（Jock Mackenzie）的苏格兰牧羊人因偷羊在这里被抓后，欧洲定居者才发现这片湖泊。当时，麦肯奇为了躲避法律制裁，把偷来的羊群藏匿在这座小镇中。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;\">传说中的蒂卡波蓝。用“人间静土”来形容特卡波湖，最为贴切不过，它远离凡尘，平静无浪、清澈见底的湖面倒映着四周常年积雪的南阿尔卑斯山脉(Southern Alps)。</span><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:8080/NewZealand//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180924/1537761037373034243.jpg\" title=\"1537761037373034243.jpg\" alt=\"1360x[2].jpg\" width=\"674\" height=\"540\"/></p>', '1537760962887', '1537761049645', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('1b68dfd6f6cd41f39a4a14a90794a57a', 'e16640f28eef444e80003f7a5f450f0e', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21', '3', '1', '净土鲁冰花绽放 : 新西兰', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">10月份从加拿大归来还在自诩今年出国游的三地恰好是南美洲欧洲北美洲最大国，话音未落，突然又有个机会要到新西兰来，那就又要換个说法&nbsp;:&nbsp;嗨！一年游了“五大洲”(包括从亚洲出发)&nbsp;。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">有一种蓝，就叫新西兰！&nbsp;这是魔戒、霍比特人的拍摄地，现实中的中土世界，长白云的故乡，上帝留下的最后一块自留地------如果天堂存在，应该是新西兰的样子！&nbsp;新西兰，我确是带心从西来！</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624647288092613.jpg\" title=\"1545624647288092613.jpg\" alt=\"100u0n000000e2gf37884_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">许多人认为怀赫科是奥克兰最奇妙的一部分,而且只要乘渡轮就可以轻松到达,美丽的海滩和原生森林保护区,加上咖啡厅、葡萄园和艺术工作坊,和谐地融为一体。怀赫科岛还是购物、品酒一日游的绝佳地点,也适合数天完全放松的度假。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">因为一个特殊原因却成就我去了趟一般中国游客决不会去的奥克兰海湾的宝地——怀赫科岛。&nbsp;朦胧诗主要代表人物&nbsp;顾城&nbsp;退职隐居后就是在激流岛上与妻子过着自给自足的生活。&nbsp;不少中国游客慕名而来，为了看一看这个中国著名诗人曾经生活的地方，但大多数来此度假的游客，他们的目的是来享受美酒和美景，我是后者。</p><p><br/></p>', '1545624625217', '1545624700326', null);
