INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('a04d50d045264f2db1d88817fe35125b', 'e16640f28eef444e80003f7a5f450f0e', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21', '3', '1', '南半球，秋意浓 | 新西兰环岛自驾亲子游', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">一直对&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;非常向往，可能是南半球的风总伴着神秘，让人捉摸不透。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">这个漂浮在南太平洋上的国家，四面都被大海包围，不与任何邻国接壤，也不容易受到外界的侵扰。几乎所有去过&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;的人都对这个国家的空气和环境赞不绝口，像是被广袤的海洋净化过，没有污染，更不用说沙尘暴、PM2.5了。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">太喜欢这个国家纯净的空气了，而这样的自然生态无疑是最适合亲子游的。尤其是看了《爸爸去哪儿》的宣传，以及黄磊夫妇带上孩子的&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;旅行，发现了好多适合小朋友的游玩项目。&nbsp;比如&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/southisland25056.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25056_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">南岛</a>的&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/akaroa57930/21860.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_57930_sii21860_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">阿卡罗阿</a>&nbsp;羊驼牧场、&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/kaikouradistrict57947/133983.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_57947_sii133983_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">凯库拉</a>&nbsp;观鲸、TSS蒸汽船，以及<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/northisland25055.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25055_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">北岛</a>的&nbsp;怀托摩&nbsp;萤火虫洞、霍比屯、&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/rorotua682.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_682_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">罗托鲁瓦</a>&nbsp;等。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">心动不如行动吧，做足了攻略后，为我们家3岁多的念念精心设计了这趟&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;亲子游。选择了5月错峰的深秋季节，<a class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/southisland25056.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25056_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">南岛自驾</a>的方式，以及带娃相对轻松的行程安排。念念还带上了&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;航空的好朋友“几维鸟Pete”一起出发！几维鸟Kiwi&nbsp;Bird是&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;的国鸟，没有翅膀所以看起来非常呆萌，也因为不会飞而成为了&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;航空的常客哦。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624977577083699.jpg\" title=\"1545624977577083699.jpg\" alt=\"10020t000000il41pF819_R_800_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p>', '1545624917290', '1545624985255', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('bd13447dd3014297a28dd39968aeb032', 'e16640f28eef444e80003f7a5f450f0e', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21', '3', '1', '新西兰第一次就该这么玩，14天南北岛户外体验之旅', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">凛冽的寒风，浑浊的空气让我愈发想念夏天的味道，总想找个地方去过冬，可是又不太想去东南亚了，我打量着世界地图，把目光移到了南半球这片从未涉足的土地，这时候一个小目标就出现了：走，<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3640758_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>去过冬！</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">25岁，人生又多了许多第一次，温度刚刚好，即使夏季也非常清凉！各种新奇刺激的户外活动，徒步步道，野生动物，驾驶着汽车穿行在南<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/northisland25055.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3640758_25055_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">北岛</a>的自然风光当中，还有美酒和海鲜作陪，也算是我2018年开年的一份厚礼～</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624808373069788.jpg\" title=\"1545624808373069788.jpg\" alt=\"100u0q000000g1ydbCC2C_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"743\" height=\"415\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>瓦纳卡孤独之树与钢琴师</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624841517052159.jpg\" title=\"1545624841517052159.jpg\" alt=\"100h0q000000g3b2x2BC7_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"458\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">《指环王》当中唯一保留的拍摄场景</span></p>', '1545624785145', '1545624871278', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('bf94594e1b6446838fcae64dabf289f7', 'e16640f28eef444e80003f7a5f450f0e', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21', '3', '1', '新西兰新旅游日记', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">基督城大教堂位于市中心，是基督城的主要标志和重要建筑之一。其始建于1864年，到1904年才真正完工，其间曾经历了三次地震。这是座哥特式建筑，高达63公尺的尖塔堪称是基督城最重要的地标，尖塔上仿英国圣保罗教堂装置了12座钟，可演奏出不同的优美旋律。我们到达后一看，只见其已破败不堪，前半部包括著名的尖塔已被2011年2月22日的大地震完全损毁，居然至今仍未修复，据说修复比重建还要费钱，有可能被完全拆除。大教堂被围档挡住了，无法拍摄到全貌，倒是大教堂前的广场比较热闹，卖唱的下地棋的晒太阳的，广场前有观光</span><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/christchurch695/67257.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3607831_695_sii67257_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">有轨电车</a><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">驶过，为城市增添了一道独特的风景。<img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:8080/NewZealand//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180921/1537475751928036972.jpg\" title=\"1537475751928036972.jpg\" alt=\"u=1311126381,3777491634&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0[1].jpg\"/></span></p>', '1537475722667', '1537475761442', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('cdb5545df2d045129ca053383ec7153d', '0b5af9b1102d4345a85fda0ead326c0a', 'aced76a43d6c46ffa58daec57f2dd6fe', '3', '1', '☆梦萦那年南半球的夏天，我们在新西兰的漫时光☆ 13天新西兰南岛自驾之旅', '<p><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/new-zealand/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">长白云之乡，中土世界，魔戒净土，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">它是人间仙境，咫尺天堂。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">雪山，湖泊，大海，<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJZ1FvBzFTYw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">冰川</a>，峡湾，鲁冰花，草泥马...</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">赤道以南，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">这个不大的南半球岛国，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">竟然齐集了这么多自然景物。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">上帝无疑是太偏心!</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">当我们从压力山大的城市来到新西兰，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">这里就像一个忘忧国，让你暂时忘却尘世间的烦忧。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">然后，回到这尘土的世界太久，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">又再想念着地球另一边那春光明媚。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">虽然已距那处人间仙境一万八千里，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">但仍然午夜梦萦那年南半球的仲夏，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们在新西兰度过的美好时光。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/akko/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">阿卡</a>罗阿宁静的海湾，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">特卡波湖畔古朴的牧羊人教堂，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">纯洁的库克山，惊艳的普卡湖，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">巍峨的皇冠山脉，漫山遍野的鲁冰花，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">若隐若现的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/milford-sound/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">米尔福德峡湾</a>，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">大名鼎鼎的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/queenstown/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">皇后镇</a>，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">在<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJalFjBzdTZw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">格林诺奇</a>，湖面升腾的那片神秘雾霭。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">静谧而璀璨的星空，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">壮美辽阔的南大平洋，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJa1FnBzRTZw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">海滩</a>上的海狮，暗洞里的小企鹅，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">路上偶遇的草泥马和羊群,</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">独特的<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.cn%2F%3Faf%3D104561116%26c%3DBBSKEYWORDS&hotel_name=Airbnb+%E7%88%B1%E5%BD%BC%E8%BF%8E\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">民宿</a>，温情的Kiwi人民...</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">满满念念不忘的记忆，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">在此篇游记里将这些珍藏于心底的记忆和照片一起融入文字，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">一幕幕展开...</p><p><br/></p>', '1537761682892', '1537761706851', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('f094a8ccf5b645aea5f364f8a9935071', 'd6174743f4694ef39710ea3715c50efb', '9ed2ca0c740e46e3a4a5184f477acf64', '3', '1', '旅游日记', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">抵达基督城的时候，是个艳阳天。四月的新西兰已是秋天，空气中有丝丝凉意。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我穿着一件白色短袖，外面披着酒红色的长款外套。背着包，拖着一件二十寸的登机箱，风尘仆仆的从机场赶到<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.cn%2F%3Faf%3D104561116%26c%3DBBSKEYWORDS&hotel_name=Airbnb+%E7%88%B1%E5%BD%BC%E8%BF%8E\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">民宿</a>。不带滤镜和修饰的旅途总是有些狼狈的，就像现实与梦想的距离一样。头发被大风吹的凌乱。开车<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJZ1FiBzNTbA/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">十分</a>钟的距离，步行约四十分钟。一路步行抵达了预订好的House，房东名叫Yu，是一名<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/china/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国</a>女人，来自河南。刚来新西兰一年，陪孩子上小学。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">House一共有三个房间，一个大客厅和户外花园。外面种满了花草，还有几支玫瑰。我的房间很大，看起来很干净，只是夜晚穿着凉鞋走在木地板上会发出很大的摩擦声。木门或许因为年久失修而不好开关。不过人在旅途，也没那么多讲究。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">差不多下午五六点钟的光景，我央求Yu带我去市中心转一圈，并允诺支付一些额外的交通费。她爽快的答应了。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们先是去了『纸板大教堂』。此时天色渐暗，教堂里早已亮起了灯。教徒们虔诚的在教堂里唱诵念经，表情庄严而肃穆。我的心也跟着安静了下来，站在一旁默默的看着，被这种信仰的力量所打动。这时的教堂被温暖包裹着，充满了安详的氛围，让人忍不住多留一会儿。可日暮即将西沉，趁着夜晚正式来临之前，还想多去一些地方，不得不离开。这也是旅行中的无奈之处吧。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:8080/NewZealand//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180924/1537760723352023478.jpg\" title=\"1537760723352023478.jpg\" alt=\"1360x[1].jpg\" width=\"610\" height=\"467\"/></p><p>在火车站与Yu分别，我坐上了开往格雷茅斯greymounth的火车。车厢比较宽敞，两旁都有巨大的观景玻璃窗。座位旁边坐着一名外国男子，名叫Ib，来自<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/denmark/\" target=\"_blank\">丹麦</a>。闲聊中竟然得知我们都就读于澳大利亚同一所大学，并且都位于黄金海岸校区，只不过他主修医学，我则在商学院。同样是一个人独自旅行，他问我接下来的行程，于是我把冰川小镇的行程简单概述了一下，他则留在格雷茅斯附近。</p><p><br/></p><p>过道另一旁的座位上坐着两名亚裔女子，后来得知她们都是工作假期来游玩的中国人，在上海工作。这时火车开始缓缓启动了，一路经过森林，山谷和平地。遇见成群牛羊，看见大片农场。在大家都兴致勃勃拍照的时候，那名女子还在抱着电脑处理客户合同，焦头烂额的样子。聊天时才发现她是一名律师。</p><p><br/></p><p>无论是在工作也好，在学校也罢。大家来到这里大部分是为了暂时逃避现有的生活吧。不想要一成不变的日子，于是有了旅行，去别人待腻了的地方转上一圈，留下些许足迹。 火车平稳的在山谷之间行驶，我感到一阵口渴，起身去餐车买了一瓶矿泉水。最后一节车厢只坐了寥寥几个人。透明的车窗一直延伸到天花板，视线好极了，我一阵心动。车上没有固定坐在某一个位子的规定，于是跟丹麦小哥打好招呼后，独自坐在了末尾的车厢里。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '1537760604349', '1537760827940', null);
INSERT INTO `cn_note` VALUES ('f6db4ade31364c2d92fa381f61cf0953', 'e16640f28eef444e80003f7a5f450f0e', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21', '3', '1', '文艺女青年领队老年养生团自驾新西兰南岛', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>的原住民是毛利人，但理论上讲毛利人也是移民，只不过他们移得很早。在大航海时代，这里被一个荷兰航海家发现，但这荷兰人在岸边跟毛利人打了一架，岸都没上就逃走了，只给这片土地留下了“新西兰”这个名字。一百年后，随着库克船长的到来，新西兰被英国殖民，迎来大批英国移民，成为日不落帝国最早升起太阳的国家。1947年独立，成为英联邦成员国，本质上跟英国没什么关系了，只是国旗上的米字图案向世界展示着新西兰过去与英国的关系。实际上新西兰政府多年来一直想要摆脱被殖民痕迹，更换米字旗，但民众却认为没这必要，大部分人都投了反对票。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>在南半球，跟咱们气候正好相反。一年四季都适合旅行，夏季暖和但不炎热，冬季寒冷但能滑雪。旺季是11月到次年3月，5月底到10月是滑雪季。携老带幼的建议选择暖和的时间出发。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">【提示】新西兰气候多变，我出发前几天<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/queenstown684.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_684_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">皇后镇</a>还在下大雪，所以带的大部分是秋冬装。结果到了新西兰没两天就升温，我就两三件夏装，只好每晚洗了穿。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545625070029075668.jpg\" title=\"1545625070029075668.jpg\" alt=\"100w0q000000g80np739C_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p>', '1545625008181', '1545625074618', null);

