INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('0503d584192944a09178c3e463ce563b', '旅游日记', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">抵达基督城的时候，是个艳阳天。四月的新西兰已是秋天，空气中有丝丝凉意。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我穿着一件白色短袖，外面披着酒红色的长款外套。背着包，拖着一件二十寸的登机箱，风尘仆仆的从机场赶到<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.cn%2F%3Faf%3D104561116%26c%3DBBSKEYWORDS&hotel_name=Airbnb+%E7%88%B1%E5%BD%BC%E8%BF%8E\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">民宿</a>。不带滤镜和修饰的旅途总是有些狼狈的，就像现实与梦想的距离一样。头发被大风吹的凌乱。开车<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJZ1FiBzNTbA/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">十分</a>钟的距离，步行约四十分钟。一路步行抵达了预订好的House，房东名叫Yu，是一名<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/china/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国</a>女人，来自河南。刚来新西兰一年，陪孩子上小学。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">House一共有三个房间，一个大客厅和户外花园。外面种满了花草，还有几支玫瑰。我的房间很大，看起来很干净，只是夜晚穿着凉鞋走在木地板上会发出很大的摩擦声。木门或许因为年久失修而不好开关。不过人在旅途，也没那么多讲究。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">差不多下午五六点钟的光景，我央求Yu带我去市中心转一圈，并允诺支付一些额外的交通费。她爽快的答应了。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们先是去了『纸板大教堂』。此时天色渐暗，教堂里早已亮起了灯。教徒们虔诚的在教堂里唱诵念经，表情庄严而肃穆。我的心也跟着安静了下来，站在一旁默默的看着，被这种信仰的力量所打动。这时的教堂被温暖包裹着，充满了安详的氛围，让人忍不住多留一会儿。可日暮即将西沉，趁着夜晚正式来临之前，还想多去一些地方，不得不离开。这也是旅行中的无奈之处吧。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:8080/NewZealand//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180924/1537760723352023478.jpg\" title=\"1537760723352023478.jpg\" alt=\"1360x[1].jpg\" width=\"610\" height=\"467\"/></p><p>在火车站与Yu分别，我坐上了开往格雷茅斯greymounth的火车。车厢比较宽敞，两旁都有巨大的观景玻璃窗。座位旁边坐着一名外国男子，名叫Ib，来自<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/denmark/\" target=\"_blank\">丹麦</a>。闲聊中竟然得知我们都就读于澳大利亚同一所大学，并且都位于黄金海岸校区，只不过他主修医学，我则在商学院。同样是一个人独自旅行，他问我接下来的行程，于是我把冰川小镇的行程简单概述了一下，他则留在格雷茅斯附近。</p><p><br/></p><p>过道另一旁的座位上坐着两名亚裔女子，后来得知她们都是工作假期来游玩的中国人，在上海工作。这时火车开始缓缓启动了，一路经过森林，山谷和平地。遇见成群牛羊，看见大片农场。在大家都兴致勃勃拍照的时候，那名女子还在抱着电脑处理客户合同，焦头烂额的样子。聊天时才发现她是一名律师。</p><p><br/></p><p>无论是在工作也好，在学校也罢。大家来到这里大部分是为了暂时逃避现有的生活吧。不想要一成不变的日子，于是有了旅行，去别人待腻了的地方转上一圈，留下些许足迹。 火车平稳的在山谷之间行驶，我感到一阵口渴，起身去餐车买了一瓶矿泉水。最后一节车厢只坐了寥寥几个人。透明的车窗一直延伸到天花板，视线好极了，我一阵心动。车上没有固定坐在某一个位子的规定，于是跟丹麦小哥打好招呼后，独自坐在了末尾的车厢里。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 'f094a8ccf5b645aea5f364f8a9935071', '27', '0', '1537760827945', '1537760827945', '1', 'rose', '9ed2ca0c740e46e3a4a5184f477acf64');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('37ddf724379546358998cfd1d4dd6314', '净土鲁冰花绽放 : 新西兰', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">10月份从加拿大归来还在自诩今年出国游的三地恰好是南美洲欧洲北美洲最大国，话音未落，突然又有个机会要到新西兰来，那就又要換个说法&nbsp;:&nbsp;嗨！一年游了“五大洲”(包括从亚洲出发)&nbsp;。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">有一种蓝，就叫新西兰！&nbsp;这是魔戒、霍比特人的拍摄地，现实中的中土世界，长白云的故乡，上帝留下的最后一块自留地------如果天堂存在，应该是新西兰的样子！&nbsp;新西兰，我确是带心从西来！</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624647288092613.jpg\" title=\"1545624647288092613.jpg\" alt=\"100u0n000000e2gf37884_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">许多人认为怀赫科是奥克兰最奇妙的一部分,而且只要乘渡轮就可以轻松到达,美丽的海滩和原生森林保护区,加上咖啡厅、葡萄园和艺术工作坊,和谐地融为一体。怀赫科岛还是购物、品酒一日游的绝佳地点,也适合数天完全放松的度假。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px 30px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">因为一个特殊原因却成就我去了趟一般中国游客决不会去的奥克兰海湾的宝地——怀赫科岛。&nbsp;朦胧诗主要代表人物&nbsp;顾城&nbsp;退职隐居后就是在激流岛上与妻子过着自给自足的生活。&nbsp;不少中国游客慕名而来，为了看一看这个中国著名诗人曾经生活的地方，但大多数来此度假的游客，他们的目的是来享受美酒和美景，我是后者。</p><p><br/></p>', '1b68dfd6f6cd41f39a4a14a90794a57a', '5', '0', '1545624700331', '1545624700331', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('5d98bdab90ac456790df48dbc06bc126', '文艺女青年领队老年养生团自驾新西兰南岛', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>的原住民是毛利人，但理论上讲毛利人也是移民，只不过他们移得很早。在大航海时代，这里被一个荷兰航海家发现，但这荷兰人在岸边跟毛利人打了一架，岸都没上就逃走了，只给这片土地留下了“新西兰”这个名字。一百年后，随着库克船长的到来，新西兰被英国殖民，迎来大批英国移民，成为日不落帝国最早升起太阳的国家。1947年独立，成为英联邦成员国，本质上跟英国没什么关系了，只是国旗上的米字图案向世界展示着新西兰过去与英国的关系。实际上新西兰政府多年来一直想要摆脱被殖民痕迹，更换米字旗，但民众却认为没这必要，大部分人都投了反对票。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>在南半球，跟咱们气候正好相反。一年四季都适合旅行，夏季暖和但不炎热，冬季寒冷但能滑雪。旺季是11月到次年3月，5月底到10月是滑雪季。携老带幼的建议选择暖和的时间出发。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">【提示】新西兰气候多变，我出发前几天<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/queenstown684.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3633252_684_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">皇后镇</a>还在下大雪，所以带的大部分是秋冬装。结果到了新西兰没两天就升温，我就两三件夏装，只好每晚洗了穿。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545625070029075668.jpg\" title=\"1545625070029075668.jpg\" alt=\"100w0q000000g80np739C_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p>', 'f6db4ade31364c2d92fa381f61cf0953', '8', '0', '1545625074623', '1545625074622', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('66819ae1a1064c6b9911c77cf450dcf5', '4位老人新西兰南岛20天3400公里的自驾之旅', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其实今天没啥好写的，一切都在计划中，都在预料中。本来觉得往东南飞嘛，很快就会天亮，可是</span><a class=\"bbsLmLabel\" href=\"https://z.qyer.com/deal/90455/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); display: inline; height: auto; left: auto; margin-right: 2px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-decoration-line: none; top: auto; width: auto;\">飞机</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">外面一直是黑的，后来才发现，舷窗的颜色是可调的。经过十几小时的飞行，飞机正点到达基督城机场。本来很担心入境时被查，网上很多告诫甚至警告，做攻略时入境卡怎么填写就很纠结，保险起见，带的所有药品都有医生的处方，登山鞋在入境单上也打了勾，生怕带了什么违禁物品（入境</span><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2EJZFFvBzRTYFI-/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">卡什</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">么填后面会细说），以至于上了飞机后还把一次性</span><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2MJYFFuBz9TZg/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">筷子</a><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">丢掉了。</span><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其实。。。其实什么都没有发生。。。。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">忘记为了什么，当我们入境时已经人不多了。入境官只是在入境单药品和登山鞋打钩的地方做了些标记，就放行了，没有开包检查，也没有看到其他人被开包检查，一个都没有。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">程程已经在等候我们了。这次出游的第一天全靠程程帮忙，出国有人接机的感觉真好，谢谢程程。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">本来我们预定的车是RAV4，属于中型SUV，可是到了停车场看到的是逍客，属于小型车了，当时心情就很不爽，有被骗的感觉。和<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"http://z.qyer.com/car/?utm_source=c03729731-pc&utm_medium=partner&utm_campaign=article&utm_content=%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">租车</a>公司联系后答复，老板故意给调整了一辆空间大的车，这不是胡扯吗。现在已经是下班时间了，又是周末，换车的话还不知道要等到什么时候，还好行李能勉强放得下，只好凑付开了，后来还车时经过交涉给我们退了133纽币。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;拿到车后简单检查了一下，就上路了，在南半球开右舵车的第一次就这么奉献了。由于在国内做了充分的准备，开右舵车也没觉得有特别不适应，就是有时雨刷和转向灯开始的时候容易弄反（关于开车后面有专门攻略）。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">接下来就是入住酒店、去超市购物和吃晚饭了，程程请我们在一家<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/china/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国</a>餐馆吃了一顿丰盛的晚餐，没想到这顿晚餐成了我们20天最奢侈的一顿。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们的住宿主要是在<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com%2F%3F%26aid%3D355694%26si%3Dai%252Cco%252Cci%252Cre%252Cdi%26label%3Dguid__datetime_15355794134793_aaid_355694-post-keyword%26lang%3Dzh-cn%26ifl%3D%26ss%3D&hotel_name=Booking.com+%E7%BC%A4%E5%AE%A2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">Booking</a>上预定的。关于住宿网上的介绍很多，有便宜的也有贵的，本游记就不做专门介绍了，关于超市后面会有介绍。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;\">今天的路线，从右上角基督城到左边的蒂卡波湖，总共230公里。住Lake Tekapo Motels &amp; Holiday Park (特卡波湖汽车旅馆和假日公园)。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;刚到蒂卡波，还没入住，先欣赏下美景。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;蒂卡波湖“既是湖的名字也是小镇的名字。小镇的北面是碧绿的湖水，湖对岸就是雄伟的南阿尔卑斯山。岩石粉顺着山上的冰河流入湖内，悬浮在湖中，使<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/lake-tekapo/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">蒂卡普湖</a>呈现出浓郁的碧绿色。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">毛利人是最早居住在麦肯奇盆地的人。他们用石头作为工具，捕捞鳗鱼，捕猎鸟类，沿河岸和湖岸建立了许多夏季营地。直到19世纪中叶一个叫麦肯奇（Jock Mackenzie）的苏格兰牧羊人因偷羊在这里被抓后，欧洲定居者才发现这片湖泊。当时，麦肯奇为了躲避法律制裁，把偷来的羊群藏匿在这座小镇中。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;\">传说中的蒂卡波蓝。用“人间静土”来形容特卡波湖，最为贴切不过，它远离凡尘，平静无浪、清澈见底的湖面倒映着四周常年积雪的南阿尔卑斯山脉(Southern Alps)。</span><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:8080/NewZealand//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180924/1537761037373034243.jpg\" title=\"1537761037373034243.jpg\" alt=\"1360x[2].jpg\" width=\"674\" height=\"540\"/></p>', '1153a1587ba74ed28d63b7975610a30b', '11', '0', '1537761049650', '1537761049650', '0', 'rose', '9ed2ca0c740e46e3a4a5184f477acf64');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('6d7d1435c5324f7f9191afb24e04a60f', '新西兰新旅游日记', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">基督城大教堂位于市中心，是基督城的主要标志和重要建筑之一。其始建于1864年，到1904年才真正完工，其间曾经历了三次地震。这是座哥特式建筑，高达63公尺的尖塔堪称是基督城最重要的地标，尖塔上仿英国圣保罗教堂装置了12座钟，可演奏出不同的优美旋律。我们到达后一看，只见其已破败不堪，前半部包括著名的尖塔已被2011年2月22日的大地震完全损毁，居然至今仍未修复，据说修复比重建还要费钱，有可能被完全拆除。大教堂被围档挡住了，无法拍摄到全貌，倒是大教堂前的广场比较热闹，卖唱的下地棋的晒太阳的，广场前有观光</span><a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/christchurch695/67257.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3607831_695_sii67257_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">有轨电车</a><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">驶过，为城市增添了一道独特的风景。</p>', 'bf94594e1b6446838fcae64dabf289f7', '13', '0', '1537475761447', '1537475761447', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('725eaebb2b434c09ba6518c0bc5ae1fa', '上山下海穿云破雾 | 新西兰14天蜜月自驾游', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;\">写在前面</span></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">“曾经沧海难为水，除却巫山不是云”，在<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/new-zealand/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>的十三天，每一天都在挑战尖叫指数。新西兰的美美的没有止境，每当我以为它已经美到了极致不可能再有更美的景致的时候，下一站它就给我放个大招，让我不得不又一次感叹自然造物的神奇；新西兰的美美的没有定式，壮丽的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJZ1FvBzFTYw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">冰川</a>，如画的峡湾，起伏的山脉，广袤的平原，亚热带雨林，以及绵延数英里长的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJa1FnBzRTZw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">海滩</a>，真真一派多彩多姿包罗<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/vientiane/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">万象</a>的风情。加上气候宜人、空气优质、人烟稀少，更为这绝美的景色增添了难得的原生态味道，以致于在今后很长一段时间里它都将是我心心念念的旅行目的地。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">这一次的新西兰蜜月旅行，时间有限而想去的地方太多，行程经历了反复多次的修改，从去北岛看火山地貌改成了去南岛观鲸，从毛利人的本土文化改成了魔戒之旅，最终将主行程定在了南岛。因为北岛典型的地貌特征是火山地热，例如著名的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/tongariro-national-park/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">汤加里罗国家公园</a>；而南岛的地貌特征则主要是冰川，景致都是冰川演化而来的湖泊河流，同时又不乏山川雨林。俗语说智者乐水，仁者乐山，我可能是个智者吧（心虚的笑~）。虽然主行程安排在南岛，但通往南岛的城市都要转机，选择直飞的话只能从<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/auckland/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">奥克兰</a>进出，因而我们专门在北岛安排了一站霍比特村游。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">以下是这次的行程安排：</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day1：上海（14:14）—奥克兰（06:40+1）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day2：抵达奥克兰，游览<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2UJZ1FgBzdTZQ/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">伊甸山</a>（宿奥克兰）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day3：霍比特村+怀托萤火虫洞（宿奥克兰）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day4：奥克兰—<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/christchurch/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">基督城</a>（宿基督城）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day5：<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2UJY1FkBzFTYFI3/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">凯库拉观鲸</a>（宿基督城）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day6：基督城—特卡波湖（宿特卡波湖）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day7：特蒂卡波湖—<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2EJZVFuBzJTbFI9/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">库克山国家公园</a>（宿库克山）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day8：<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2UJY1FkBz5TYFI6/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">塔斯曼冰川</a>+<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJalFhBzJTYQ/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">普卡基湖</a>+<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/oamaru/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">奥马鲁</a>—<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/dunedin/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">但尼丁</a>（宿但尼丁）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day9：但尼丁+奥塔哥半岛（宿但尼丁）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">Day10：但尼丁-<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/queenstown/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">皇后镇</a>（宿皇后镇）</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);