INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('836f313201134775b8d5815ac5ff1848', '☆梦萦那年南半球的夏天，我们在新西兰的漫时光☆ 13天新西兰南岛自驾之旅', '<p><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/new-zealand/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">长白云之乡，中土世界，魔戒净土，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">它是人间仙境，咫尺天堂。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">雪山，湖泊，大海，<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJZ1FvBzFTYw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">冰川</a>，峡湾，鲁冰花，草泥马...</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">赤道以南，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">这个不大的南半球岛国，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">竟然齐集了这么多自然景物。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">上帝无疑是太偏心!</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">当我们从压力山大的城市来到新西兰，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">这里就像一个忘忧国，让你暂时忘却尘世间的烦忧。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">然后，回到这尘土的世界太久，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">又再想念着地球另一边那春光明媚。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">虽然已距那处人间仙境一万八千里，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">但仍然午夜梦萦那年南半球的仲夏，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">我们在新西兰度过的美好时光。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/akko/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">阿卡</a>罗阿宁静的海湾，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">特卡波湖畔古朴的牧羊人教堂，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">纯洁的库克山，惊艳的普卡湖，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">巍峨的皇冠山脉，漫山遍野的鲁冰花，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">若隐若现的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/milford-sound/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">米尔福德峡湾</a>，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">大名鼎鼎的<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/queenstown/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">皇后镇</a>，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">在<a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJalFjBzdTZw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">格林诺奇</a>，湖面升腾的那片神秘雾霭。</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">静谧而璀璨的星空，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">壮美辽阔的南大平洋，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"bbsPlaceLabel\" href=\"https://place.qyer.com/poi/V2wJa1FnBzRTZw/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-decoration-line: none;\">海滩</a>上的海狮，暗洞里的小企鹅，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">路上偶遇的草泥马和羊群,</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">独特的<a class=\"bbsBizLabel\" href=\"https://hotel.qyer.com/goto.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.cn%2F%3Faf%3D104561116%26c%3DBBSKEYWORDS&hotel_name=Airbnb+%E7%88%B1%E5%BD%BC%E8%BF%8E\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 115, 182);\">民宿</a>，温情的Kiwi人民...</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">满满念念不忘的记忆，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">在此篇游记里将这些珍藏于心底的记忆和照片一起融入文字，</p><p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">一幕幕展开...</p><p><br/></p>', 'cdb5545df2d045129ca053383ec7153d', '13', '0', '1537761706856', '1537761706856', '0', 'mengmeng', 'aced76a43d6c46ffa58daec57f2dd6fe');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('955d88073770428ea517761c36d36045', '新西兰十一天旅游日记（1）', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">第一天、上海浦东</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">11月30日，上海多云。上午8时从家乡乘坐大巴前往<a class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://flights.ctrip.com/booking/airport-pudong/#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3607831_fli-por3_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">上海浦东机场</a>。9时30分抵达，办理了领取外币及移动WiFi手续，在T2航站楼等候。中午11时许，携程领队应婷婷召集大家，此行共有31人，应婷婷麻利地给大家发护照和登机牌，交代了注意事项，并建了微信群，把31人按家庭分好了组。很短时间内就处理好一切事项，彰显了其的精明强干，也让大家领略了其直爽干脆的性格。有这么一位领队，此行一定会非常顺利。然后排队托运行李，过边境检查和安全检查。下午14点15分新西兰航空的NZ288航班准点起飞，飞机是波音787机型，座位是3+3+3的格局，虽是经济舱，但座位不显得是那么的拥挤逼仄，机上服务员大多是华人，语言沟通无障碍。机上娱乐设施有中文界面，不少电影有中文字幕，原本下载在手机上的电影电视剧都派不上用场了。享用了机上晚餐和2杯红酒后，昏昏睡去。</p><p><br/></p>', '526a85f97bde4684935f169b9b0a9920', '1', '0', '1545623571904', '1545623571904', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('c9e27ff3ca274b11a8f7d32ceabd1eaa', '新西兰第一次就该这么玩，14天南北岛户外体验之旅', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">凛冽的寒风，浑浊的空气让我愈发想念夏天的味道，总想找个地方去过冬，可是又不太想去东南亚了，我打量着世界地图，把目光移到了南半球这片从未涉足的土地，这时候一个小目标就出现了：走，<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3640758_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>去过冬！</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">25岁，人生又多了许多第一次，温度刚刚好，即使夏季也非常清凉！各种新奇刺激的户外活动，徒步步道，野生动物，驾驶着汽车穿行在南<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/northisland25055.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3640758_25055_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); color: rgb(0, 134, 180); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">北岛</a>的自然风光当中，还有美酒和海鲜作陪，也算是我2018年开年的一份厚礼～</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624808373069788.jpg\" title=\"1545624808373069788.jpg\" alt=\"100u0q000000g1ydbCC2C_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"743\" height=\"415\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>瓦纳卡孤独之树与钢琴师</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624841517052159.jpg\" title=\"1545624841517052159.jpg\" alt=\"100h0q000000g3b2x2BC7_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"458\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\">《指环王》当中唯一保留的拍摄场景</span></p>', 'bd13447dd3014297a28dd39968aeb032', '6', '0', '1545624871282', '1545624871282', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('cb6ec3a38bd44c92a8774a5b8cfe3297', '新西兰美景', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>新西兰的夜景真是太美了.</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545625188168025832.jpg\" title=\"1545625188168025832.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '5819cda02a8a4a05b3cde86ae375ba5b', '8', '0', '1545625211154', '1545625211153', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('ce28b355fd5247a7a567b47dce42cb67', '新西兰十一天旅游日记（2）', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">第二天、奥克兰、基督城、布伦纳湖</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">12月1日，奥克兰时间早晨6时 (北京时间凌晨1时) 许，经过近11个小时的飞行，抵达了新西兰第一大城市奥克兰。在机场办理完入境手续去提取行李，然后过海关检查。新西兰对动植物的检疫检查非常重视，这在飞机上填写入境卡时应领队就反复交代过的，要我们一定要如实申报。在排队等候期间，同机抵达的已移民新西兰的一位华人指着墙上大幅的中文标语“这是你最后的机会”八个大字，告诉我新西兰人注重诚信，只要你如实申报并将违禁物品丢弃则不会影响入境，否则后果非常严重，并说曾有一位大妈独自探望在新西兰做月子的女儿，带了一只火腿，不想扔掉侥幸过关，哪知被查到后将人扣留，下个航班就遣返回国了，且永远不给签证。在新西兰过海关确实与其它国家不同，比澳大利亚还要严格，有一个海关官员逐一询问我们，好在有应领队在一旁翻译，我如实告诉所带食品无非是方便面所带药物无非是旅行日常用药等，遂顺利过关，又经X光检查后终于出关了。同行团友均顺利过关。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">出了国际航站楼，我们沿路上划的绿色线条拖着行李步行了约十五分钟到达国内航站楼，乘坐NZ531航班前往基督城，好在登机牌在上海就已办好，托运行李后过安检就登机了。飞机准点起飞，1小时20分后抵达新西兰第三大城市基督城。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p></p>', '803c194a66114a41be5e1d785863dc0f', '3', '0', '1545623671019', '1545623671019', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');
INSERT INTO `cn_post` VALUES ('d0cb49b919974a27a1ce3530d301b5bd', '南半球，秋意浓 | 新西兰环岛自驾亲子游', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">一直对&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;非常向往，可能是南半球的风总伴着神秘，让人捉摸不透。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">这个漂浮在南太平洋上的国家，四面都被大海包围，不与任何邻国接壤，也不容易受到外界的侵扰。几乎所有去过&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;的人都对这个国家的空气和环境赞不绝口，像是被广袤的海洋净化过，没有污染，更不用说沙尘暴、PM2.5了。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">太喜欢这个国家纯净的空气了，而这样的自然生态无疑是最适合亲子游的。尤其是看了《爸爸去哪儿》的宣传，以及黄磊夫妇带上孩子的&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newzealand100078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_100078_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">新西兰</a>&nbsp;旅行，发现了好多适合小朋友的游玩项目。&nbsp;比如&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/southisland25056.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25056_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">南岛</a>的&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/akaroa57930/21860.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_57930_sii21860_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">阿卡罗阿</a>&nbsp;羊驼牧场、&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/kaikouradistrict57947/133983.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_57947_sii133983_2_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">凯库拉</a>&nbsp;观鲸、TSS蒸汽船，以及<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/northisland25055.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25055_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">北岛</a>的&nbsp;怀托摩&nbsp;萤火虫洞、霍比屯、&nbsp;<a class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/rorotua682.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_682_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">罗托鲁瓦</a>&nbsp;等。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all;\">\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all;\">心动不如行动吧，做足了攻略后，为我们家3岁多的念念精心设计了这趟&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;亲子游。选择了5月错峰的深秋季节，<a class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/southisland25056.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3686712_25056_l\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 2px; text-decoration-line: none;\">南岛自驾</a>的方式，以及带娃相对轻松的行程安排。念念还带上了&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;航空的好朋友“几维鸟Pete”一起出发！几维鸟Kiwi&nbsp;Bird是&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;的国鸟，没有翅膀所以看起来非常呆萌，也因为不会飞而成为了&nbsp;新西兰&nbsp;航空的常客哦。</p><p><img src=\"http://47.105.107.52:80/../images/20181224/1545624977577083699.jpg\" title=\"1545624977577083699.jpg\" alt=\"10020t000000il41pF819_R_800_10000_Q90.jpg\"/></p>', 'a04d50d045264f2db1d88817fe35125b', '8', '0', '1545624985262', '1545624985262', '0', 'jack', '93312482b3ac43caa3ed96c0cf243d21');

